Label: “No supplement” indicator
Description: An empty element that provides a positive indication there is no alternative ‘generic’ supplement to be used in cases where there is a vendor-specific supplement (indicated using <SalesOutlet> with the same <SequenceNumber> specified within the Supplement manifest). The empty <NoSupplement/> must be used – and must only be used – when no <BodyManifest> is present within the Supplement manifest.
